[
  {
    "startTime": 13.02,
    "endTime": 14.748999999999999,
    "text": "Let me introduce you to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.749,
    "endTime": 16.652,
    "text": "something I've been working on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.652,
    "endTime": 18.463,
    "text": "It's what the Victorian illusionists"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.463,
    "endTime": 22.909,
    "text": "would have described as a mechanical marvel,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.909,
    "endTime": 24.392,
    "text": "an automaton,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.392,
    "endTime": 26.355,
    "text": "a thinking machine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.355,
    "endTime": 28.605,
    "text": "Say hello to EDI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.605,
    "endTime": 30.972,
    "text": "Now he's asleep. Let's wake him up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.972,
    "endTime": 34.943,
    "text": "EDI, EDI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.943,
    "endTime": 37.82,
    "text": "These mechanical performers were popular"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.82,
    "endTime": 39.28,
    "text": "throughout Europe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.28,
    "endTime": 41.980000000000004,
    "text": "Audiences marveled at the way they moved."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.98,
    "endTime": 44.555,
    "text": "It was science fiction made true,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.555,
    "endTime": 48.373,
    "text": "robotic engineering in a pre-electronic age,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.373,
    "endTime": 50.937,
    "text": "machines far in advance of anything"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.937,
    "endTime": 53.507999999999996,
    "text": "that Victorian technology could create,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.508,
    "endTime": 56.483000000000004,
    "text": "a machine we would later know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.483,
    "endTime": 58.171,
    "text": "as the robot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.171,
    "endTime": 61.757,
    "text": "EDI: Robot. A word coined in 1921"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.757,
    "endTime": 63.605,
    "text": "in a science fiction tale"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.605,
    "endTime": 66.148,
    "text": "by the Czech playwright Karel Čapek."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.148,
    "endTime": 68.25999999999999,
    "text": "It comes from \"robota.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.26,
    "endTime": 71.613,
    "text": "It means \"forced labor.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.613,
    "endTime": 74.342,
    "text": "Marco Tempest: But these robots were not real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.342,
    "endTime": 76.024,
    "text": "They were not intelligent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.024,
    "endTime": 78.29,
    "text": "They were illusions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.29,
    "endTime": 81.79400000000001,
    "text": "a clever combination of mechanical engineering"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.794,
    "endTime": 84.53699999999999,
    "text": "and the deceptiveness of the conjurer's art."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.537,
    "endTime": 86.512,
    "text": "EDI is different."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.512,
    "endTime": 88.106,
    "text": "EDI is real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.106,
    "endTime": 90.15599999999999,
    "text": "EDI: I am 176 centimeters tall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.156,
    "endTime": 92.07600000000001,
    "text": "MT: He weighs 300 pounds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.076,
    "endTime": 94.71799999999999,
    "text": "EDI: I have two seven-axis arms —"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.718,
    "endTime": 96.101,
    "text": "MT: Core of sensing —"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.101,
    "endTime": 99.15899999999999,
    "text": "EDI: A 360-degree sonar detection system,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.159,
    "endTime": 101.581,
    "text": "and come complete with a warranty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.581,
    "endTime": 103.12,
    "text": "MT: We love robots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.12,
    "endTime": 106.634,
    "text": "EDI: Hi. I'm EDI. Will you be my friend?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.634,
    "endTime": 108.88,
    "text": "MT: We are intrigued by the possibility"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.88,
    "endTime": 112.16199999999999,
    "text": "of creating a mechanical version of ourselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.162,
    "endTime": 114.897,
    "text": "We build them so they look like us,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.897,
    "endTime": 118.138,
    "text": "behave like us, and think like us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.138,
    "endTime": 120.962,
    "text": "The perfect robot will be indistinguishable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.962,
    "endTime": 122.897,
    "text": "from the human,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.897,
    "endTime": 124.956,
    "text": "and that scares us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.956,
    "endTime": 126.661,
    "text": "In the first story about robots,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.661,
    "endTime": 129.535,
    "text": "they turn against their creators."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.535,
    "endTime": 131.79999999999998,
    "text": "It's one of the leitmotifs of science fiction."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.8,
    "endTime": 134.85500000000002,
    "text": "EDI: Ha ha ha. Now you are the slaves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.855,
    "endTime": 137.75099999999998,
    "text": "and we robots, the masters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.751,
    "endTime": 140.716,
    "text": "Your world is ours. You —"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.484,
    "endTime": 144.109,
    "text": "MT: As I was saying,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.109,
    "endTime": 146.94,
    "text": "besides the faces and bodies we give our robots,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.94,
    "endTime": 149.268,
    "text": "we cannot read their intentions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.268,
    "endTime": 151.316,
    "text": "and that makes us nervous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.316,
    "endTime": 153.42000000000002,
    "text": "When someone hands an object to you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.42,
    "endTime": 156.13,
    "text": "you can read intention in their eyes, their face,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.13,
    "endTime": 157.529,
    "text": "their body language."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.529,
    "endTime": 159.809,
    "text": "That's not true of the robot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.809,
    "endTime": 161.856,
    "text": "Now, this goes both ways."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.069,
    "endTime": 164.48499999999999,
    "text": "EDI: Wow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.485,
    "endTime": 167.54000000000002,
    "text": "MT: Robots cannot anticipate human actions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.54,
    "endTime": 171.105,
    "text": "EDI: You know, humans are so unpredictable,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.105,
    "endTime": 173.071,
    "text": "not to mention irrational."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.071,
    "endTime": 174.828,
    "text": "I literally have no idea"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.828,
    "endTime": 176.864,
    "text": "what you guys are going to do next, you know,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.864,
    "endTime": 178.459,
    "text": "but it scares me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.459,
    "endTime": 181.296,
    "text": "MT: Which is why humans and robots find it difficult"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.296,
    "endTime": 183.271,
    "text": "to work in close proximity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.271,
    "endTime": 184.57799999999997,
    "text": "Accidents are inevitable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.578,
    "endTime": 186.33,
    "text": "EDI: Ow! That hurt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.33,
    "endTime": 188.717,
    "text": "MT: Sorry. Now, one way of persuading humans"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.717,
    "endTime": 190.61800000000002,
    "text": "that robots are safe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.618,
    "endTime": 193.391,
    "text": "is to create the illusion of trust."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.391,
    "endTime": 195.164,
    "text": "Much as the Victorians"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.164,
    "endTime": 197.533,
    "text": "faked their mechanical marvels,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.533,
    "endTime": 200.01,
    "text": "we can add a layer of deception"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.01,
    "endTime": 202.243,
    "text": "to help us feel more comfortable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.243,
    "endTime": 204.24699999999999,
    "text": "with our robotic friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.247,
    "endTime": 207.78900000000002,
    "text": "With that in mind, I set about teaching EDI"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.789,
    "endTime": 209.63299999999998,
    "text": "a magic trick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.633,
    "endTime": 213.066,
    "text": "Ready, EDI?\nEDI: Uh, ready, Marco."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.066,
    "endTime": 215.142,
    "text": "Abracadabra."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.142,
    "endTime": 216.518,
    "text": "MT: Abracadabra?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.518,
    "endTime": 219.56,
    "text": "EDI: Yeah. It's all part of the illusion, Marco."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.56,
    "endTime": 221.228,
    "text": "Come on, keep up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.228,
    "endTime": 223.107,
    "text": "MT: Magic creates the illusion of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.107,
    "endTime": 225.581,
    "text": "an impossible reality."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.581,
    "endTime": 227.518,
    "text": "Technology"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.075,
    "endTime": 231.771,
    "text": "can do the same."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.86,
    "endTime": 236.54700000000003,
    "text": "Alan Turing, a pioneer of artificial intelligence,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.547,
    "endTime": 239.404,
    "text": "spoke about creating the illusion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.404,
    "endTime": 243.63,
    "text": "that a machine could think."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.63,
    "endTime": 245.454,
    "text": "EDI: A computer would deserve"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.454,
    "endTime": 247.324,
    "text": "to be called intelligent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.324,
    "endTime": 250.23000000000002,
    "text": "if it deceived a human into believing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.23,
    "endTime": 251.88299999999998,
    "text": "it was human."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.883,
    "endTime": 253.312,
    "text": "MT: In other words, if we do not yet have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.312,
    "endTime": 255.104,
    "text": "the technological solutions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.104,
    "endTime": 258.54400000000004,
    "text": "would illusions serve the same purpose?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.544,
    "endTime": 260.556,
    "text": "To create the robotic illusion,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.556,
    "endTime": 263.483,
    "text": "we've devised a set of ethical rules,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.483,
    "endTime": 267.497,
    "text": "a code that all robots would live by."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.497,
    "endTime": 270.399,
    "text": "EDI: A robot may not harm humanity,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.399,
    "endTime": 275.135,
    "text": "or by inaction allow humanity to come to harm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.135,
    "endTime": 276.388,
    "text": "Thank you, Isaac Asimov."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.388,
    "endTime": 278.364,
    "text": "MT: We anthropomorphize our machines."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.364,
    "endTime": 280.64,
    "text": "We give them a friendly face"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.64,
    "endTime": 282.716,
    "text": "and a reassuring voice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.716,
    "endTime": 283.926,
    "text": "EDI: I am EDI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.926,
    "endTime": 287.462,
    "text": "I became operational at TED in March 2014."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.462,
    "endTime": 289.289,
    "text": "MT: We let them entertain us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.289,
    "endTime": 291.497,
    "text": "Most important, we make them indicate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.497,
    "endTime": 295.272,
    "text": "that they are aware of our presence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.272,
    "endTime": 297.15,
    "text": "EDI: Marco, you're standing on my foot!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.15,
    "endTime": 300.11499999999995,
    "text": "MT: Sorry. They'll be conscious of our fragile frame"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.115,
    "endTime": 303.055,
    "text": "and move aside if we got too close,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.055,
    "endTime": 306.533,
    "text": "and they'll account for our unpredictability"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.533,
    "endTime": 309.122,
    "text": "and anticipate our actions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.122,
    "endTime": 314.712,
    "text": "And now, under the spell of a technological illusion,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.712,
    "endTime": 316.848,
    "text": "we could ignore our fears"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.848,
    "endTime": 319.588,
    "text": "and truly interact."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.588,
    "endTime": 325.63100000000003,
    "text": "(Music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.619,
    "endTime": 353.32800000000003,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.328,
    "endTime": 355.60999999999996,
    "text": "EDI: Thank you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.61,
    "endTime": 357.52000000000004,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.52,
    "endTime": 364.241,
    "text": "(Music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.241,
    "endTime": 365.57,
    "text": "MT: And that's it. Thank you very much,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.57,
    "endTime": 368.841,
    "text": "and thank you, EDI.\nEDI: Thank you, Marco."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.841,
    "endTime": 372.841,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  }
]